        "start": 152.48,
        "duration": 4.88
    },
    {
        "text": "the nucleus of the cell proteins",
        "start": 155.36,
        "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
        "text": "meanwhile are made outside the nucleus",
        "start": 157.36,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "the solution",
        "start": 159.92,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "is to copy out the instructions and send",
        "start": 160.72,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "a message outside the nucleus you might",
        "start": 162.8,
        "duration": 3.519
    },
    {
        "text": "see where this is going",
        "start": 165.12,
        "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
        "text": "that message is made of messenger rna",
        "start": 166.319,
        "duration": 4.801
    },
