        "start": 179.76,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "message into a protein",
        "start": 181.92,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "this is where the clever part comes in",
        "start": 183.36,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "because we know the genetic code",
        "start": 185.04,
        "duration": 4.479
    },
